<div class="d-flex justify-content-between dashboard-layout">
  <div class="flex-column ml-3 mt-3">
    <div id="dashboard-profile" class="text-center">
      <h3>Welcome<br>
         <%= current_user.name %></h3>
      <p>Today is <em><%= Date.today.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></em></p>
      <p class="time"><%= Time.now.strftime("%H:%M") %></p>
      <% @counter = 0 %>
      <% current_user.messages.each do |message| %>
        <% message.comments.each do |comment| %>
          <% comment.status == "unread" ? @counter += 1 : @counter %>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
      <% if @counter == 0 %>
      <p>You do not have any unread comments</p>
      <% elsif @counter == 1 %>
      <p><i class="fas fa-bell" style="color: red;"></i> You have <strong style="color: red"><%= @counter %></strong> unread comment</p>
      <% else %>
      <p><i class="fas fa-bell" style="color: red;"></i> You have <%= @counter %> unread comments</p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center mt-4">
    <div class="cards">
      <figure class="image-block mx-2">
        <h1>Bulletin Board</h1>
        <img src="<%= image_path 'dashboard/bulletinboard.jpg' %>" alt="" />
        <figcaption>
          <h3 class="text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
          </h3>
          <p>Check the events the school has planned and make sure you do not miss any of the activities your child is involved in.</p>
          <%= link_to "Go to the board", events_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="image-block mx-2">
        <h1>Notebook</h1>
        <img src="<%= image_path 'dashboard/notebook.jpg' %>" alt="" />
        <figcaption>
          <h3 class="text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
          </h3>
          <p>Consult the messages teachers have left in your child's notebook and communicate with the teachers directly.</p>
          <%= link_to "Go to the notebook", student_messages_path(current_user.students), class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="image-block mx-2">
        <h1>Parent Meetings</h1>
        <img src="<%= image_path 'dashboard/meeting.jpg' %>" alt="" />
        <figcaption>
          <h3 class="text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
          </h3>
          <p>Check when is the next parent/teacher meeting and select a time slot for when you are available.<br>&nbsp;</p>
          <button class="btn btn-primary">
            Schedule meetings
          </button>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="image-block mx-2">
        <h1>Class Schedules</h1>
        <img src="<%= image_path 'dashboard/schedule.jpg' %>" alt="" />
        <figcaption>
          <h3 class="text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
          </h3>
          <p>Consult your child's schedule to make sure what time they start and finish each day so you can organize yourself.</p>
          <button class="btn btn-primary">
            Go the the schedules
          </button>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="image-block mx-2">
        <h1>Grades</h1>
        <img src="<%= image_path 'dashboard/grade.jpg' %>" alt="" />
        <figcaption>
          <h3 class="text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
          </h3>
          <p>Consult each individual grades your child got and the semester average. Confirm there that you have seen them.</p>
          <button class="btn btn-primary">
            Go to grades
          </button>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
